  <h1>Icons</h1>
  <p><code>.icon</code>. By default icons inherit color from their parent, but if desired, can be colored using <code>.icon--light</code>, <code>.icon--dark</code>, <code>.icon--a</code>, <code>.icon--b</code>, <code>.icon--c</code>, <code>.icon--d</code>, <code>.icon--e</code> and <code>.icon--f</code></p>

  <h3>Cross</h3>
  <p><code>.icon--cross</code></p>

